content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Feb 11 (APP):The joint session of Parliament initially scheduled for February 12 at 11:00 AM had been rescheduled to February 18 at 11:00 AM at the Parliament House. According to a notification from the National Assembly Secretariat the Speaker of the National Assembly made this change under the powers vested in him by the Joint Sitting Rules, 1973.
